snippet.title: The first PV of "Tokyo Ghoul: Break the Chains"
snippet.description:
Various card combos, turn the tables at any timeReal-time co-op battles, engaging in strategic fights against dreadful enemies

——Reservation Rewards Ongoing——
Make a reservation now to receive the reservation reward including [Summon Ticket*10]
Rewards will be even greater if the number of reservations keeps going up. Hurry up and invite your friends to make reservations~
